         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">25, WILTON PLACE. S.W. ¶ May 15 /73 ¶ My dear Sir ¶  ¶ I have delayed writing to you till the last day in the hopes of being able to announce to you the arrival of the box of inferior ovary Monocotyle...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">73.05.15a</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">From George Bentham</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">RB MSS M3, Library, Royal Botanic Gardens Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="form%20text" style="color: #2f5496; font-family: Times, Times; ">25, WILTON PLACE. S.W.</seg>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">May 15 /73</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">My dear Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>I have delayed writing to you till the last day in the hopes of being able to announce to you the arrival of the box of inferior ovary Monocotyledons — but the Hampshire is not yet among the arrivals<note xml:id="ftn1" type="footnote" n="1">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>See M to G. Bentham, 1 March 1873 (in this edition as 73-03-01a).</p>
               </note> In the mean time your <name key="Orchideae">Orchideae</name> were sent off from Kew the week before last and I trust you will receive them safe — After them it will still require three or four hundred species to make up the volume so that after all I may be obliged to make the volume a short one. You will have received eight sheets<note xml:id="ftn2" type="footnote" n="2">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Bentham (1863-78), vol. 6, sheets B – I, i.e. pp. 1-128.</p>
               </note> I think and three or four more are in type.</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>You will have seen our friend Mr George Macleay<note xml:id="ftn3" type="footnote" n="3">
                  <p rend="Footnote"
                     style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; margin-left: 0.3335in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: -0.3335in; font-size: 9pt; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Macleay had delivered to M a case of deciduous trees from Kew, see M to J. Hooker, 25 March 1873.</p>
               </note> He is much interested in your welfare and I hope you may find his friendly counsel of use in guiding you as to the best means of getting rid of your present annoyances</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">Yours ever truly</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; margin-right: 0in; text-indent: 0in; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>George Bentham</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-family: Geneva, Geneva; font-size: 12pt; "
               xml:lang="en">Baron Ferd v. Mueller</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="plant%20names" xml:lang="en">
               <name key="Orchideae">Orchideae</name>
            </p>
